者，處 3 年以上 10 年\r\n以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1017%2c20220324%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,交簡,1017,20220324,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1017","JDATE":"20220324","JTITLE":"公共危險"}